				Ok enough is enough.  For all those people that think saying they are leaving on a public forum is going to make it verant or soe lose sleep and make an apologetic retraction suddenly and undo all the changes they have made.  Your pathetic.<BR>
I come to everlore to talk about things happening with the game.  I just found out what the patch was actually about and in a way, yeah it sucks.  But on the other hand they are making changes so that everyone in the game is getting a better shot at having fun.  I dont think mages should be turned into gods nor do i think that monks should be turned into useless chunks of living vomit for everyone to beat up on.  Monks dont have it that bad now. after the patch things may get a little tougher. but the end justifies the means and i say good job verant.  Two thumbs up.  <BR>
<BR>
Oh yeah and as far as the clerics are concerned most people dont lvl past 25 before they grow tired of a character.  im gonna go out on a limb and say that 80+% of the clerics made in the game have never caught a glimpse of the full heal spell.  So less than 20% of the clerics in the game are now upset because they cant heal that extra 1k hp in one shot(thats assuming that they have even meet someone with over 7500 hp), cmon think about it.  <BR>
<BR>
The patch scales down the power of a few classes...oh well... when we all started the game alot of this stuff wasnt available anyway yet we still played.  Taking away something that made more complications and agitations anyway!!! OMG not that.<BR>
~  Damn you verant for making things better.  Sometimes i wonder what a pay less than an hourly wage for a month..~<BR>
<BR>
&quot;Its my story.  Thats right my story my world.  You dont like what i have to say close the book. In the end i allready got paid.&quot; -Johnny Turbo-<BR>
<BR>
&quot;Sometimes people need to sit back and look at the big picture.  Once they pull their heads out of there arses  they will figure out the problems in the past arent worth worrying about nearly as much as the speeding car heading straight for them is.&quot;<BR>
<BR>
