				yeah, frankly i am getting tired of all of the changes introduced lately.  As a 53 druid, its difficult to find a group.  Now, as of a few months after luclin came out, you wouldn't believe my surprise and disgust when i saw the message *this monster is immune to root/speed spells*.  I cursed eq and verant.  Now these damn mobs are appearing all over.  So here I am, and druid that can't get a group and can't solo the mobs i want to.  All i have to say is that Verant should seriously think about what they are doing and tread lightly.  They have alot of competition around the corner, Earth and Beyond, Shadowbane, Acherion's call 2, not to mention others.  If things continue into the fact you HAVE NO CHOICE BUT TO GROUP, then i will be leaving eq soon myself.  How can a casual player cope?  sorry, just my rantings and ravings.  :) 
