				     I agree, soloing now sucks, and grouping isn't any better unless you have a full group. At high lvls it is near impossible to get into a good lasting group anywhere decent. I spent 11 hours this weekend with a full group in Velks, with steady pulls, and only got about 4 blues of AA the whole time. If I solo, the 1 pixil of blue every other kill I used to get turns into 1 pixil every 4 or so. Also the fact that everything that is being changed is being done for the 2 or 3 big guilds that exist on each server. The majority of the people who play are not in these &quot;uber&quot; guilds. Yes the new druid heal is great for raids, It helps the healers a LOT, but now the &quot;uber&quot; guild can do anything and basicly claim the world at a whim.. and smaller guilds are at a disadvantage because of numbers again. <BR>
